code: @Override public String getSpringBootVersion() {     for (DependencyManagement delegate : this.delegates) {         String version = delegate.getSpringBootVersion().         if (version != null) {             return version.         }     }     return null. }

@Override public Dependency find(String artifactId) {     for (DependencyManagement delegate : this.delegates) {         Dependency found = delegate.find(artifactId).         if (found != null) {             return found.         }     }     return null. }
